# Use the grep tool:
grep -pattern "ICircuitBreakerService" -path "BE/AmesaBackend.Lottery/Program.cs" -C 3
```

**Examples of what to ask instead:**
- ‚ùå Bad: "Run `git show HEAD:BE/AmesaBackend.Lottery/Program.cs | Select-String -Pattern 'ICircuitBreakerService'`"
